room_title: Escape room "Chapel de Puzzled" by Puzzled Escape Rooms in Fargo
room_address: 114 Broadway N Suite L1 Fargo, ND 58102
room_description: Your best friend is getting married but it turns out the best man is in love with the bride. He has hidden the marriage certificate and the officiant won't marry them without it. You have to search the Chapel de Puzzled and find the marriage certificate so that your friend can get married on time. The wedding is in an hour. Can you find it in 60 minutes?
